steps.name: Given I am login on staging env by created timestamp project
Debug step:
When I navigate to menu "Mobile app" with submenu "Mobile Editor"
Then I should see Mobile screen display
When I select tab name Pages with index 1
When I add new screen with name JIT037FormPreviewCode
Then I should see the screen with name JIT037FormPreviewCode display in list Pages
When I select screen with name JIT037FormPreviewCode
When I select tab list with name "Layers"
When I open Search popup on item value "JIT037FormPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I add item "Form" in Search popup with sub menu "Form" to preview mobile editor
When I open preview code with component mode
Then I should see the code content "M37a_MAIN_FORM_INIT"
When I close preview code panel
When I toggle on item value "JIT037FormPreviewCode" with index "1"
When I select item value "Form" with index "1"
When I toggle off Layout tree header
When I update field label "Width" of header "Basic" with radio "%" and value "100"
When I update field label "Height" of header "Basic" with radio "%" and value "100"
When I update field label "Flex" of header "Basic" with value "0.8"
When I select the color for field label "Background Color" of header "Basic" by inputting the hexcode value "#FF0000"
When I select the color for field label "Border Color" of header "Basic" by inputting the hexcode value "#0007FF"
When I select dropdown field label "Border Style" of header "Basic" with value "solid"
When I update field label "Radius" of header "Basic" with radio "PX" and value "20"
When I update field label "Border Width" of header "Basic" with value "10"
When I select field label "Flex Direction" of header "Layout" with radio "column"
When I select field label "Direction" of header "Layout" with radio "ltr"
When I select field label "Flex Wrap" of header "Layout" with radio "nowrap"
When I select dropdown field label "Justify Content" of header "Layout" with value "center"
When I select dropdown field label "Align Items" of header "Layout" with value "flex-start"
When I select dropdown field label "Align Self" of header "Layout" with value "flex-end"
When I select dropdown field label "Align Content" of header "Layout" with value "stretch"
When I update field label "flexBasis" of header "Layout" with value "0"
When I update field label "flexShrink" of header "Layout" with value "1"
When I update field label "flexGrow" of header "Layout" with value "2"
When I update margin-padding id "marginTop" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginLeft" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginBottom" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "marginRight" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingTop" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingLeft" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingBottom" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I update margin-padding id "paddingRight" of header "Spacing" with value "10"
When I open preview code with style mode
Then I should see the code content "M37a_STYLE_FORM"
